kthegame.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Tony Hawk Pro Skater</em> website</a> .</p><p> Now, the skateboarding legend has responded to the rumours that a new game is set to be announced March 4 at 6:30pm GMT.</p><p> “Looks like a teaser for something related to <em>Tony Hawk&#39;s Pro Skater</em> has been found in Black Ops 6&#39;s Grind MP map! Announcement on March 4,” wrote <em>Call Of Duty</em> fan account <a href="https://x.com/charlieINTEL/status/1892621320598208577" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CharlieIntel</a> on X before both <a href="https://x.com/tonyhawk/status/1892622967579832757" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hawk</a> and the official <a href="https://x.com/Xbox/status/1892643631141388678" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox</a> account replied with the side eye emoji. </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="qme" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f440.png" alt="👀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> — Tony Hawk (@tonyhawk) <a href="https://twitter.com/tonyhawk/status/1892622967579832757?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 20, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “Please Mr. Tony sir, <em>American Wasteland</em> remastered please,” <a href="https://x.com/atomx626/status/1892959306858791215" target="_blank" rel="noopener">wrote</a> one fan. “Never played <em>Tony Hawk&#39;s Pro Skater 3 &amp; 4</em> , so you have no idea how excited I would be if they&#39;re remaking those 2 games,” <a href="https://x.com/METALGOD2K/status/1892676212893376711" target="_blank" rel="noopener">said</a> another.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-celebrates-25th-anniversary-of-pro-skater-promises-series-has-a-future-3798182">Reflecting on the legacy of <em>Tony Hawk&#39;s Pro Skater</em> last year</a> , Hawk wrote: My intention and expectation for the game was mostly for the enjoyment of skateboarders. I had no idea it would transcend a niche market to become a massive success and – as some have argued – change the course of skateboarding&#39;s popularity (and possibly even skate trick evolution). It definitely changed the course of my life, and is a big reason that I get to ride my skateboard for a living to this very day. And most of the featured characters are still out there ripping and representing skateboarding&#39;s diversity in the best ways possible.”</p><p> In other news, <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones">Game Of Thrones</a></em> author <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-r-r-martin">George RR Martin</a> has confirmed there is “some talk” of an <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">Elden Ring</a></em> movie – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/george-r-r-martin-elden-ring-movie-game-of-thrones-delay-3840707">but he might not be involved</a> because he still has a book to finish.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/tony-hawk-responds-to-rumours-of-a-new-pro-skater-game-3840736">Tony Hawk responds to rumours of a new &#39;Pro Skater&#39; game</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
